definition: abbr. for Xinjiang 新疆[Xin1 jiang1] or Singapore 新加坡[Xin1 jia1 po1]/surname Xin

sentences.english: How many Northern Ireland Protestants vote for Sinn Fein?

sentences.english: All the parties to the peace process, including Sinn Fein, denounced the bombing.
